  <heading>FRSQRTE</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Floating-point reciprocal square root estimate (unpredicated)</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction finds the approximate reciprocal square root of each active floating-point element of the source vector,
and places the results in the corresponding elements of the destination vector.
This instruction is unpredicated.</para>
    </authored>
    <predicated>False</predicated>
  </desc>
